    <b>Hello!</b> I'm Mateusz Bis, a dedicated and versatile <b>Full Stack Software Engineer</b> with a robust
    background in both development and design.
  </p>
  <p>
    I' been present in the tech world since <b>2019</b> when I created{" "}
    <a href="https://redinnlabs.com" target="_blank" class="gradient-text">Redinn</a>, a <b>web agency</b> which to this
    day puts performance and quality at the forefront of every project. I've experienced working in a variety of
    environments, from <b>startups</b> (<a href="https://poznajgory.pl" target="_blank" class="gradient-text">Poznaj
    GÃ³ry</a>),
    through <b>middle-size companies</b> (<a href="https://optimamedical.com" target="_blank" class="gradient-text">Optima
    Medical</a>)
    to <b>corporate settings</b> (<a href="https://avsystem.com" target="_blank" class="gradient-text">AVSystem</a>).
  </p>
  <p>
    Throughout the years, I've gained experience across a variety of domains, including development of <b>
    websites</b>,{" "}
    <b>web & native apps</b>, <b>backend microservices</b>, and utilization of{" "}
    <b>AWS & Google Cloud</b>. Many of my skills are not only proven by my projects shown below, but also by <b>various
    certifications</b> visible on
    my{" "}
    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mateusz-bis-185bb1230/" target="_blank" class="gradient-text">
      LinkedIn profile</a>.
  </p>
  <p>
    I'm also a dedicated student of{" "}
    <a href="https://informatyka.agh.edu.pl/en/" target="_blank" class="gradient-text">
